Firstly, download the attachment and configure your E-mail client:
$ tar xvf ~/Download/powertool-alpha-x.tar.bz2
$ cd powertool-alpha-x
$ ./powertool
$ gedit ~/.msmtprc
and replace the line "password ???" with your real password

Secondly, report your work with the PowerTool:
$ ./powertool -r install
$ ./powertool -r command
